Class ExtensionValuesStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.jupiter.engine.execution.ExtensionValuesStore

  • @API(value=Internal)
public class ExtensionValuesStore
extends java.lang.Object
    ExtensionValuesStore is used inside implementations of ExtensionContext to store and retrieve attributes with get(org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ExtensionContext.Namespace, java.lang.Object), put(org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ExtensionContext.Namespace, java.lang.Object, java.lang.Object), or getOrComputeIfAbsent(org.junit.jupiter.api.extension.ExtensionContext.Namespace, java.lang.Object, java.util.function.Function<java.lang.Object, java.lang.Object>).
